{
  "stem": "13469.5",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a hospital, and some of the best doctors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because Dutch Jewish doctors, they-- they would be deported to Westerbork, and they would be kept back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People like that were also kept back-- people who-- who were good dentists or good doctors, and they would provide the facilities in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Another category of people-- I must come back to my story in a minute-- but another category of people that were kept back in Westerbork were people who were good artists, musicians, et cetera, because they had an orchestra there.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They had cinema.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They had-- what's it called, can't think of the name now-- but anyway, theater shows.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And all those sort of things, because some of the best artists from-- from Holland were Jews, and all stayed in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they were kept back, kind of thing-- not sent for deportation, so they could entertain us, kind of thing.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that was all available.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but it was all available.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we could go for walks, we could play football in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So generally, it wasn't really so bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no official school that we remember, or official Jewish instruction.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But there probably was unofficially schools, and-- and religious instruction.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The problem was that the people of the right age to give the instruction were working during the day, so they would have to do it in the evening.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, the other thing was there was plenty of food in-- in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no problem there, nobody died starvation.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "In fact, nobody died in Westerbork at all, except from normal causes, as you would normally from various illnesses.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There were no diseases, nothing like that in Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
